nvidia-graphics-drivers-364 (364.15-0ubuntu1~gpu16.04.2) xenial; urgency=medium

  * debian/copy-nvidia-options, debian/rules:
    - Make sure to copy the file itself in /etc/modprobe.d rather
      than copying a link to it.
    - Enable KMS by default.
  * debian/templates/nvidia-graphics-drivers.dirs.in,
    debian/templates/nvidia-graphics-drivers.grub-gfxpayload.in,
    debian/templates/nvidia-graphics-drivers.install.in,
    debian/templates/nvidia-graphics-drivers.postinst.in:
    - No longer blacklist nvidia cards in Grub.

